# ---- Large media: NEVER commit videos to GitHub ----
# (GitHub blocks files >100MB; Pages caps the site ~1GB / 100GB-mo bandwidth)
# Videos are served from object storage + CDN — see video-config.js
*.mp4
*.mov
*.webm
*.m4v
*.avi

# ---- Dev/session artifacts (not part of the site) ----
screenshots/
uploads/
_pdftmp/
assets/deck/
# assets/g = raw 4K gallery PNGs (12–24MB each), no longer rendered
# (the site now uses the optimized assets/s set) — kept locally, off Git
assets/g/

# ---- OS / editor / temp junk ----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.tmp
*.tmp.*
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
node_modules/

# ---- Local-only secrets (keep API keys out of a public repo) ----
# assistant-config.js   # <- uncomment & host the key in a serverless proxy if you ever add a real key
